<https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/SEC/Debt/CollateralizedDebtObligations/>
	a owl:Ontology ;
	rdfs:label "Collateralized Debt Obligations Ontology"@en ;
	dcterms:abstract "Collateralized debt obligations are tranched debt instruments based on pools of debt instruments, and those pools may have different management styles and objectives. Generally includes an equity tranche. This ontology also covers CDO squared." ;
